          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "### A Transaction with ID {frequentBackendXminnum} is Impeding Autovacuum from Cleaning up Dead Tuples.\r\nServer is using prepared transactions, this transaction may be associated with an **Orphaned Prepared Transaction** on the Server. Please check the prepared transaction section for more Information on this Issue.\r\n\r\n**OR**\r\n\r\nThis Transaction may be Associated with an **Inactive Replication Slot or high replication lag** on the Server. Please Check the **Inactive Replication Slot and Replicaiton lag** section for more information on this issue.\r\n\r\n**OR**\r\n\r\nThe Transaction ID causing the issue may be associated with a long-running session on the replica server. Please Check the **Long running transactions on replica servers with hot_standby_feedback=ON** section for more information on this issue.",
              "style": "warning"
            },
            "conditionalVisibilities": [
