          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "\r\n<h6>*Find the description of each metric below. *</h6>\r\n\r\nParamater | Description\r\n--- | ---\r\n**DatabaseName** | Name of the database.\r\n**PercentTowardsWraparoundProtection** | how much % of the trasaction ID's left before the database server enters into wrap around protection mode (it gets shut down and does not accept any new transactions).\r\n**PercentTowardsEmergencyAV** | how much % of transaction ID's left before the database server runs aggressive autovacuum.\r\n**PercentTowardsWraparoundMxid** | how much % of multi transaction ID's left before the database server goes into wrap-around.\r\n**PercentTowardsEmergencyAVMxid**| how much % of multi transaction ID's left before the database server runs aggressive autovacuum.\r\n"
